=Episode 15=
(She is My Princess)

3
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,600
Enough, enough, stop.

4
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,120
Spit it out.

5
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,000
Is the one in this portrait

6
