10
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,079
Your Majesty.

11
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:45,520
Why not just kill this spy?

12
00:00:46,399 --> 00:00:47,200
Your Majesty.

13
00:00:47,359 --> 00:00:49,520
I suffered such humiliation
because of her.

14
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:51,399
You must stand up for me.

15
00:00:54,039 --> 00:00:55,280
Keep beating her

16
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,359
until she confesses.

17
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,119
Wait a moment.

18
00:01:23,924 --> 00:01:27,475
♪Clear starlight♪

19
00:01:27,475 --> 00:01:30,528
♪Spread across your brows♪

20
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,799
Your Majesty

21
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,840
I created this drawing.

22
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,239
I and Princess of Sheng

23
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,799
once had a brief encounter.

24
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,599
But she was wearing a veil.

25
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:48,159
I sketched her looks from a guess.

26
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:51,239
The resemblance isn't always precise.

27
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:55,439
But she is indeed Princess of Sheng
whom I am to marry.

28
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,519
Your Majesty, don't listen to him.

29
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,319
You shut up

30
