♪Deep feelings, but shallow fate♪

31
00:02:14,592 --> 00:02:20,480
♪Longings are just persistent♪

32
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:24,896
♪It's been a rough ride♪

33
00:02:25,216 --> 00:02:28,704
♪Even drifting clouds have the wind♪

34
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:31,072
♪Hold your sword♪

35
00:02:31,072 --> 00:02:35,488
♪Face to face, yet words escape♪

36
00:02:35,904 --> 00:02:39,456
♪Lament this short life♪

37
00:02:39,456 --> 00:02:43,712
♪Shall we vow
to reunite in the next life♪

38
00:02:43,712 --> 00:02:49,952
♪In this life,
a red thread for you is all I get♪

39
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,439
If Empress Dowager has doubts,

40
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,960
check my mansion please.

41
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,719
Your Majesty.

42
