♪Clear starlight♪

43
00:03:24,275 --> 00:03:27,040
♪Spread across your brows♪

44
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,216
♪Invite a crescent moon♪

45
00:03:29,216 --> 00:03:34,208
♪Walking in your footsteps♪

46
